#### iOS Projects [RemindMe](http://duliodenis.github.io/RemindMe/) - Reminder App #### CS193P Winter 2013 Assignments These are my solutions to the first three assignments in the Stanford iOS Course:
[HW 0](https://github.com/duliodenis/cs193p-Winter-2013-hw0) - Card Flipping App Demo walkthrough
[HW 1](https://github.com/duliodenis/cs193p-Winter-2013-hw1) - Matchismo card matching game baseline
[HW 2](https://github.com/duliodenis/cs193p-Winter-2013-hw2) - Matchismo with second card game: Set
[HW 3](https://github.com/duliodenis/cs193p-Winter-2013-hw3) - Matchismo with custom UIView subclasses, UICollectionView, and AutoLayout
#### Support or Contact Visit [ddApps](http://ddApps.co) to see more.
